dct_description_sm: Map of Europe lacking international boundaries or country names, probably published sometime during World War I.
[Ges. Gesch. Nachdruck verboten. D.R.G.M a. ; Druck u. verlag TM Wendisch Berlin. 68].
Shows major waterways and cities, sea routes.
